{"lemma":"نِعْماتُ","slug":"نِعْماتُ","root":"ن.ع.م","root_slug":"ن-ع-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ع-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نِعْمَة","root":"نعم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":50},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n44044","n44051","n44052","n44053"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%90%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"blessing, grace, benefit","examples":[{"text":"وَمَا بِكُم مِّن نِّعْمَةٍ فَمِنَ اللَّهِ ۖ ثُمَّ إِذَا مَسَّكُمُ الضُّرُّ فَإِلَيْهِ تَجْأَرُونَ","english":"Whatever blessings you have are from Allah. Then whenever hardship touches you, to Him ˹alone˺ you cry ˹for help˺."},{"text":"وَٱفْتَنَّ فِيكَ ٱلنَّاظِرُونَ؛ فَإِصْبَعٌ / يُومَا إِلَيْكَ بِهَا، وَعَيْنٌ تَنْظُرُ\nيَجِدُونَ رُؤْيَتَكَ ٱلَّتِي فَازُوا بِهَا / مِنْ أَنْعُمِ ٱللّٰهِ ٱلَّتِي لَا تُكْفَرُ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/niʕ.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44044","headword_ar":"نَعَّمَهُ","root":"nEm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAEamahu","text_ar":"نَاعَمَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(God, S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him to enjoy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lead, a plentiful, and a pleasant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an easy, and a soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicate, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"life; a state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"life, of ease and plenty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naE~amahu","text_ar":"نَعَّمَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He nourished well him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it; pampered him."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","God"]},{"entry_id":"n44051","headword_ar":"نَعْمَةٌ","root":"nEm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subst. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanaE~umN","text_ar":"تَنَعُّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraf~upN","text_ar":"تَرَفُّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subst. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamat~uEo","text_ar":"تَمَتُّعْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanaE~umN","text_ar":"تَنَعُّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S: in F's smaller copy,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanaEiymN","text_ar":"تَنَعِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", an evident mistake:) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plentifulness, and pleasantness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easiness, and softness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicacy, of life: ease and plenty."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEomapN","text_ar":"نَعْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A living in"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enjoyment of a life of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"softness, daintiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicacy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ease, comfort,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affluence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEiymN","text_ar":"نَعِيمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutoEapN","text_ar":"مُتْ